# Golden OpenAPI specs for the spectest round-trip harness must stay LF on every
# platform. Without this, Windows checkouts with autocrlf=true would convert them
# to CRLF, and the byte-exact golden comparisons in internal/spectest would drift
# (the test also normalizes EOL as a second line of defense, but pinning the
# checkout is the primary guarantee).
internal/spectest/testdata/**/*.yaml text eol=lf
